{"tid":998541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"14歲少女產子！兒生父竟是她9歲弟","createTime":"2019-01-28T05:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T23:40:28.000Z","uid":131917,"like":196,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"90362c50e0ccc7c56deff674b97c6826bb511209","tid":998541,"uid":131917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/14%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%A2%E5%AD%90-%E5%85%92%E7%94%9F%E7%88%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B99%E6%AD%B2%E5%BC%9F-014108072.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F14%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%25A2%25E5%25AD%2590-%25E5%2585%2592%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2588%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B99%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25BC%259F-014108072.html&d=8FWVfFAHAUFKZ2pbkJ9dxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=c0162329\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/14%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%A2%E5%AD%90-%E5%85%92%E7%94%9F%E7%88%B6%E7%AB%9F%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%B99%E6%AD%B2%E5%BC%9F-014108072.html</a><br />\n14歲少女產子！兒生父竟是她9歲弟<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/28/131107_d8ec28f813c99b293183e1dc51c73b89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F28%2F131107_d8ec28f813c99b293183e1dc51c73b89.jpg&h=0ec245bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在社會風氣越來越開放，也讓青少年初次性行為的年齡越來越低，日本近日還瘋傳一張「未滿14歲少女生產」統計表，發現最年輕的媽媽只有10歲，更誇張的是，其中一名14歲少女懷孕生子原因，竟是因為和9歲的弟弟發生性行為，讓網友看了全都嚇傻。<br />\n<br />\n日本論壇近日傳出一張，日本某地區未滿14歲少女生子的統計表，只見表格中除了遭性侵以及和長輩發生性關係外，有些少女是因為和兄弟亂倫才會產子，其中最年輕的10歲小媽媽就是因為和13歲的哥哥上床才會懷孕。另外，更吸引人注目的是，一名14歲國中女學生懷孕生子的原因，竟是因為和自己9歲的弟弟嘿咻。<br />\n<br />\n這份「小孩生小孩」的統計表讓網友全看傻眼，紛紛討論說，「這也太混亂了吧」、「10歲就生小孩？我那時候都不知道在幹嘛呢」、「這些老師是怎樣？10幾歲的都不放過」、「那麼多不明？不會都是因為性侵吧？」「9歲的弟弟真的知道自己在幹嘛嗎？」還有人發現大部分小媽媽的生產方式都是「帝王切開」，表示「年紀太小不能自然產，所以只能剖腹吧」，不過因為這份統計表未標明來源，也有不少人懷疑它的真實性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24617117ef316e94719872b5473a6b3c772c5744","tid":998541,"uid":12178,"like":778,"dislike":3,"score":775,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:13:24.000Z","msg":"帝王切開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72101e66e73a7de28dd7797003f0a92c772db1c","tid":998541,"uid":77196,"like":172,"dislike":2,"score":170,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"估錯國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a008465d888ef5de908489b431a083e6dfccfd7","tid":998541,"uid":209120,"like":18,"dislike":4,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"咁細個已經咁識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867145a4dcb71c8b943d95a086483577b9765939","tid":998541,"uid":57513,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"好似見過張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fbf87fe240876cee2424e75bfbc48cb8e07ea2","tid":998541,"uid":124730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"教畜嘅比例都唔少"},{"pid":"e0f26737411d2f4be05ff4cb0cd741532eb202ed","tid":998541,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"日本呢方面係幾勁"},{"pid":"9efaf3752520c594b5ec9c9641e73aec9e204c4c","tid":998541,"uid":202151,"like":254,"dislike":8,"score":246,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"9歲就破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幸福賓州"},{"pid":"3d32f33b74ade05ae02846ea44b9da5a7a592c18","tid":998541,"uid":6329,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"重注左新北市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393d3c1d765d1d29cb29dd20548dfd6d448b27d5","tid":998541,"uid":169289,"like":9,"dislike":78,"score":-69,"quote":{"pid":"9efaf3752520c594b5ec9c9641e73aec9e204c4c","tid":998541,"uid":202151,"li