r />\n食團年飯嗰陣<br />\n我喺抬面上面放咗一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手<br />\n叫咗聲：「多謝外公！」<br />\n<br />\n好彩唔喺街姐<br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山瞓一排<br />\n而家諗返自己真喺痴痴地線<br />\n自己比錢自己洗<br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},{"pid":"b07f1bba060bad485b61a5d79c46c4910cee91c9","tid":998541,"uid":162910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:55:25.000Z","msg":"9歲就有精"},{"pid":"e103eef9e61d6834e6a9e39eb60fc42dd096d21c","tid":998541,"uid":141176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:55:33.000Z","msg":"中一就出嚟做援交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f07f7bdc06eb826d7742a6759ebf038c64437e5","tid":998541,"uid":43897,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n<br />\n生出黎個仔個老豆係個仔既細佬？<br />\n<br />\n即係同個同細佬搞野，生左個呀哥出黎？<br />\n<br />\n我睇左d乜撚野"},{"pid":"6c2b6a045b45fc8ec4b56d15f1b55483f3728b84","tid":998541,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffca2972c34e9d5685043895f6436e1f079b501","tid":998541,"uid":182786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:59:03.000Z","msg":"全部變孤兒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05a635b04249767b69a5bf7667cfe10a4c4a11a","tid":998541,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"又話日本好多處男既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cddf68ba06ed269f1bf43ea78c46fd8c11ac989","tid":998541,"uid":43560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"中一援交 咁撚狂咁撚等錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ecbdbc2f914a6a077dce066057a33e80a46cd5","tid":998541,"uid":204923,