己都亂咗... <br />\n<br />\n食團年飯嗰陣<br />\n我喺抬面上面放咗一封一千蚊利是<br />\n再拎返封利是上手<br />\n叫咗聲：「多謝外公！」<br />\n<br />\n好彩唔喺街姐<br />\n唔係真係比人捉去青山瞓一排<br />\n而家諗返自己真喺痴痴地線<br />\n自己比錢自己洗<br />\n咪即係去自己鋪頭買野..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"好耐以前係電台聽過"},{"pid":"d4dc857390fa9a287b89725fe5a6ab2a1f373493","tid":998541,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:23:15.000Z","msg":"10歲生B簡直痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b3bb7a07e3dce4c241f7cae22229d523579c2a","tid":998541,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6c788de13ec58778d4640d66c19bf64271293a","tid":998541,"uid":28163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:02:28.000Z","msg":"咁多不明<br />\n聖母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"mixed埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a19235824fe267b83a7eca3a7e5c3a53d603b48","tid":998541,"uid":116330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:28:25.000Z","msg":"9歲個細路點樣學識屌西?"},{"pid":"33b5cf681bdfe41da825690ef334c486f8c6986f","tid":998541,"uid":23125,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0853d4a25e0c124fa646c1cef0699bbc1c31297d","tid":998541,"uid":123053,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"9歲就屌到閪<br />\n我閪毛都未掂到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:29:50.000Z","msg":"9歳最多睇緊有碼av<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170ca74dd71347a5a17505971bcd72c828d0a63a","tid":998541,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"係真唔係<br />\n九歲有成熟精子"},{"pid":"b60f84d49c7de5c6872aa300f514078fe95c3345","tid":998541,"uid":47954,"li